<h2 align="center">
<i>ConsScale</i> is a biologically-inspired scale for measuring cognitive development in natural and artificial creatures.
</h2>
<p align="center"><i>ConsScale</i> has been specifically designed for the evaluation of Machine Consciousness implementations. 
Each level is characterized by <b>architectural</b> and <b>behavioral</b> criteria.
Try the <a href="calc.html"><b><i>ConsScale</i> Calculator</a></b> to discover how creatures are rated in the scale.
</p></center>


